Copy the content of the controllers directory to the controllers directory of your rail application.
And try the services with your client using following endpoint addresses

Echo Sample                 		: http://your_rail_application/wsservice/echo
Echo with Addressing Sample 		: http://your_rail_application/wsservice/echo_addr
Echo with Reliable Messaging Sample : http://your_rail_application/wsservice/echo_reliable
Echo with Class Map Sample 			: http://your_rail_application/wsservice/echo_classmap
MTOM Sample 						: http://your_rail_application/wsservice/mtom
